OL,3,CRail disability campaigner to miss
OL,4,CRoyal Garden Party due to train strikes
OL,6,FA disability campaigner says he feels
OL,7,Ftotally let down that he'll miss out
OL,8,Fon attending the Royal Garden Party,
OL,9,Fdue to train strikes.
OL,11,FCameron Wood from Hereford was invited
OL,12,Fto the party at Buckingham Palace
OL,13,Fafter being nominated by the
OL,14,FDepartment for Transport, for his work
OL,15,Fon improving disability access across
OL,16,Fthe region's rail network.
OL,18,FMr Wood worked with railway stations
OL,19,Facross the Midlands to get better
OL,20,Faccessibility signage for those
OL,21,Fneeding assistance.
